data.description: PRICE REDUCTION! Motivated Seller! Looking for a secluded, peaceful setting! Look no more! This cute cottage is surrounded by trees with the sounds of a running creek.  This home has a total of 3 Skylights!  Located in kitchen, bedroom, and bathroom.  The living room features a wood burning stove and a vaulted ceiling.  Enjoy the outside scenery with an enclosed front porch!  The bedroom has a double closet, panel walls, and a skylight! Bathroom features tile, skylight and a walk in closet for added storage.  There is a basement (350sq ft) for extra needed storage and for washer/dryer.  This charming cottage has unlimited possibilities with some upgrades!  It would be a great home or weekend getaways!
